Package net.dempsy.config

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cluster
    Conceptually, a Cluster is the collection of all Message Processors that handle the same 'message type' across a an entire application and potentially distributed across a network.
    Cluster.EvictionFrequency  
    ClusterId
    ClusterIds are a unique Id of a message processor Cluster within a Dempsy application.
    Node
    In Dempsy parlance, a Node is the intersection of a Cluster with physical compute resources.
